  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d659aa9d-a9ff-4046-8f9b-106cadd76e8c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a747b353-a4b2-48f9-a6e7-bacb1916d98d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e593875-8765-11ed-b542-8320d8465d53\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(전문직종) 프로필명함</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e1b52773-39cf-49db-b5e6-73587055819b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c702799-80f6-4358-b4d1-7d5c062e424e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e593876-8765-11ed-b542-45c115e96443\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프로필명함의 활용도는 다양합니다. 전문직의 경우 자신의 프로필이 가장 중요한 홍보 수단일 수 있습니다. 자신의 커리어, 거래처, 키워드 등을 잘 만들면 그것처럼 좋은 홍보물이 또 없습니다. 전문분야의 커리어는 자신의 키워드속에 묻어 나고 또는 가장 잘 만든 슬로건이 가장 효과적인 홍보수단일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04d4dcb7-8fb5-4679-b28c-493578e1cb33\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f87-8765-11ed-b542-9b075feed253\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b79e536-fe41-4a9f-abc5-c259b8af301b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f88-8765-11ed-b542-6b8f142ccf74\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 소개는 방송인, 골프코치, 전문분야 강사 등 자신의 커리어나 슬로건으로 홍보를 원하는 분을 찾습니다. 자신의 전문분야 커리어가 무기인 분들이 프로필명함에서 가장 잘 만들고 활용할 수 있는 부분입니다. </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c349e2b-e961-499a-a195-f2157c9ca243\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f89-8765-11ed-b542-c9be9803ad2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2e925618-1867-40e1-aa4d-79cb588646f6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f8a-8765-11ed-b542-a16efafe8b24\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음은 16년간 스피치코칭을 하고 계신 대표님께서 의뢰하신 건입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7fbb0751-b869-4a0c-8b0f-933e1f3ad276\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f8b-8765-11ed-b542-c3c4f2ff8874\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">* 여기 디자인에 등장하는 모든 기록과 내용은 정무늬대표님의 동의를 얻어서 올려드리는 것입니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f8c-8765-11ed-b542-01809752c7a0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9fc29945-9593-40de-bb71-663cd312d68d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f8d-8765-11ed-b542-27ad8172c826\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0c57e59-4160-4406-b0f6-0d79ba587601\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba868c7e-9184-4814-80c3-482230bb6b74\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4e595f8e-8765-11ed-b542-83b1630fb275\" style=\"\">우아한스피치</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f18510d3-6ccf-4906-8d1d-39d23c5644db\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a71c8144-6a62-486b-a39c-76dce4acb12d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e595f8f-8765-11ed-b542-61703bebfdfa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db064ba2-5dd2-459c-9979-9cd206b945c3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-a73002b0-c1f8-49a7-80a9-d2c354978a98\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aff336cb-7526-41de-9f0d-1e73c11ed731\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-938b1e69-693f-4b8d-98a0-996f444a89a8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c32048a-65c0-41fc-8d81-7b8be651345e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e5986a0-8765-11ed-b542-99f2e6d228ac\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 진행 Step1</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d06269cc-7011-43f4-9a07-1d6359436909\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e5986a1-8765-11ed-b542-1d089a000a50\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이번 작업도 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 템플릿 생성의 차원에서 이미지템플릿을 만들고 정무늬대표님께 허락을 구하는 과정으로 진행하였습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 년 2,000건 이상의 작업을 목표로 작업하고 있습니다. 전문분야별로 3~5건 정도의 템플릿을 제작하고 있습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 주력상품으로 프로필명함과 포트폴리오 제작을 선점하고자 합니다. 가장 강력한 템플릿으로 경쟁하고 싶습니다. 아직은 100점짜리거나 완벽하지는 않지만 고객의 니즈(Needs)를 더욱 고려하여 발전해 나가도록 하겠습니다. 2023년에는 가장 완벽한 프로필로 여러분의 포트폴리오를 완성해 보도록하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-01e73bbd-dddb-4c8e-be2b-e6208e0dbfc6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-17641249-936a-46f0-a541-27e65ba704a8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-46f0e01f-e85d-4306-96b7-ee7b76a34280\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e5986a2-8765-11ed-b542-35e978161817\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">정무늬대표님은 저에게는 특별한 분이라 템플릿 제작 겸 시안을 3가지 드렸었습니다. 3가지중에 맨 아래 디자인을 선택하셨네요. 하지만 나머지 두가지도 조금은 다르지만 약간의 변형을 통해 활용하실 수 있게 제작해 드렸습니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e5986a3-8765-11ed-b542-c153882a0c46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88601578-ad4e-4227-ad16-fbc56c0d4153\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e5986a4-8765-11ed-b542-4d80b7f58040\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-8990237c-f1c2-4802-9e89-a8afd1bb69ab\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1138e