-11ed-b542-b7de8dba6434\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 프로필명함이 필요하다고 판단되는 전문분야입니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adbd-8765-11ed-b542-c16b3e2a5b72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bde71bda-7942-47a7-bf1c-7e1dd215ab77\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adbe-8765-11ed-b542-4d89aa11a255\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-a8bd90d2-ea88-4a5b-950e-84e7da2e96f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b3f51ca-5ace-46aa-911f-8cd942ebb8c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adbf-8765-11ed-b542-997fc05a6274\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>방송, 예술인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a539571-d830-4cd3-ba63-1086413552cc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc0-8765-11ed-b542-d52bd16a04f8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">방송인이나 예술인은 자신의 프로필이 무기일 수 있습니다. 자신의 커리어를 통해 알리고 또는 프로필영상에 자신의 음악도 삽입하실 수 있습니다. 예를 들어 첼리스트 분이라면 자신의 프로필사진과 함께 공연 계획이나 경력을 적어 프로필명함을 만드실 수 있습니다. 또한 영상에 음악을 삽입할 수 도 있습니다. 방송, 예술인 템플릿은 다음 회에 연재하도록 하겠습니다. 그리고 이 블로그를 통해 프로필명함을 의뢰해주신 방송예술인이 계시면 가장 합리적인 금액과 디자인을 선물(?)해 드리도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-17538a0a-3925-44e8-a19e-6fe15690c51f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ad01d48e-3e38-48a2-af97-4db2b3e02ba9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-288084a7-8493-4421-b1c1-b28dda4a00d1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc1-8765-11ed-b542-f3041fae7549\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc2-8765-11ed-b542-bfba2cad5231\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cec4f283-cefa-4bc3-9c04-9139d0147853\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc3-8765-11ed-b542-f1fb41d4f042\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-9a0aed2e-863a-429a-8bfa-e7758f46b142\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee44202d-f578-4216-9e06-1f340e58979a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc4-8765-11ed-b542-679789901ae6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>의사, 변호사, 세무사 등</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bdf18813-c490-429b-ab50-14d86aff89f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc5-8765-11ed-b542-67c6281c56e9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">전문분야에 계신분들은 반드시 프로필명함이 필요하시다고 판단됩니다. 아울러 프로필동영상까지 만들면 더욱 효과적일 수 있습니다. 내 프로필을 명함으로 보내지 마시고 프로필명함으로 보내보도록하십시요. 이전에 설명드린 이미지검색을 통해 더 요과적으로 활용될 수 있습니다. 이미지검색으로 더 멋진 디자인이 마치 앱처럼(?) 활용되는 방법이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4471d829-b25b-41a1-a7c7-3b8add8fd5f6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e59adc6-8765-11ed-b542-c3bc761785f1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4911eb67-1384-415f-9a47-3e1392d4d4d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d7b618ec-464d-4042-899e-e7383176df90\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0942ad34-e7a9-43aa-9195-fecdc7b1c583\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8da32c2-0984-4d6d-b4f8-47832e88b0da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222967488013/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div